%N A395948 Expansion of e.g.f. sinh(x)^2*cosh(x)*exp(x).
%C A395948 Number of strings of length n defined on {0,1,2,3} with an odd number of 0's, an odd number of 1's, an even number of 2's and no restriction on the number of 3's.
%H A395948 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A395948/b395948.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%F A395948 a(n) = 2^(n-2) * (2^(n-1) - n (mod 2)), n > 0; a(0) = 0.
%e A395948 The 120 strings of length 5 are (number of permutations in parentheses): 00013 (20), 01113 (20), 01333 (20), 01223 (60).
%t A395948 A395948[n_] := If[n == 0, 0, #*(2*# - Mod[n, 2]) & [2^(n-2)]];
